metadata.name: Crazy Little Punks 5
metadata.description: Welcome to the Crazy Little Punks home at Coinbase. Discover the best pieces from this collection. Crazy Little Punks is a collection of 50 randomly generated and stylistically selected NFTs that exist on the Ethereum blockchain. Some seem normal. Some of them look strange. And some are just damn cool! Each Crazy Little Punks is unique and contains items of varying rarity.
